@startuml Sequence_Recruiter_Authentication
title Nhà Tuyển Dụng - Đăng Ký & Đăng Nhập

actor Recruiter as "👔 Recruiter"
participant FrontEnd as "Frontend\nApp"
participant AuthService as "Auth\nService"
database Database as "Database"

== Đăng Ký Nhà Tuyển Dụng ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click "Đăng ký nhà tuyển dụng"
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: Show registration form
Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Nhập email, password, tên, công ty
FrontEnd -> AuthService: POST /api/auth/dang-ky-nha-tuyen-dung\n(email, password, hoTen, tenCongTy)
AuthService -> Database: Create tai_khoan (RECRUITER role)
Database --> AuthService: Return taiKhoanId
AuthService -> Database: Create nha_tuyen_dung
Database --> AuthService: OK
AuthService --> FrontEnd: Account created
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: ✅ Đăng ký thành công

== Đăng Nhập ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click "Đăng nhập"
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: Show login form
Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Enter email, password
FrontEnd -> AuthService: POST /api/auth/dang-nhap\n(email, password)
AuthService -> Database: Verify credentials
Database --> AuthService: OK
AuthService --> FrontEnd: Return JWT token
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: ✅ Logged in

== Đăng Xuất ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click "Đăng xuất"
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: Clear JWT
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: ✅ Logged out

@enduml
